                  <p class="card-text"><a style="color: #ffcc00; text-decoration: underline;" href="https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/justice-george-floyd-0">White House Petition:</a> Official US Government Petition
                  </p>
                  <p class="card-text"><a style="color: #ffcc00; text-decoration: underline;" href="https://www.justiceforbigfloyd.com/">Justice for Floyd:</a> Add your name
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12" style="padding-bottom: 25px;">
              <div class="card" style="width: inherit; background-color: transparent;">
                <div class="card-body" style="background-color: #2B2E32; border-radius: 15px;">
                  <h5 class="card-title" style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 30px;">Protest
                    Locations</h5>
                  <p style="color: #ffcc00; background-color: #212529; border-radius: 15px;" class="card-text text-center p-1">Boston <span><a
                        href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir//Boston,+MA/@42.3145186,-71.1103678,11z/data=!4m9!4m8!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x89e3652d0d3d311b:0x787cbf240162e8a0!2m2!1d-71.0588801!2d42.3600825!3e0">-
                        Get Directions</a></span></p>
                  <p style="color: #ffcc00; background-color: #212529; border-radius: 15px;" class="card-text text-center p-1">Framingham <span><a
                        href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir//Framingham,+MA/@42.2793442,-71.4511759,13z/data=!4m9!4m8!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x89e38838715d77df:0x9ea068cb22156362!2m2!1d-71.4161565!2d42.279286!3e0">-
                        Get Directions</a></span></p>
                </div>
                <br>
                <div class="card-body" style="background-color: #2B2E32; border-radius: 15px;">
                  <h5 class="card-title" style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 30px;">MA Social Medias
                  </h5>
                  <p style="background-color: #212529; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;" class="card-text p-1"><a href="https://twitter.com/MassGovernor">Gov. Baker</a></p>
                  <p style="background-color: #212529; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;" class="card-text p-1"><a href="https://twitter.com/MayorJenny">Mayor Walsh - Boston</a></p>
                  <p style="background-color: #212529; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;" class="card-text p-1"><a href="https://twitter.com/MassStatePolice">Massachusetts Police</a></p>
                  <p style="background-color: #212529; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;" class="card-text p-1"><a href="https://twitter.com/bostonpolice">Boston Police</a></p>

                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
        <div class="card" style="width: inherit; background-color: transparent; height: 500px;">
          <div class="card-body" style="background-color: #2B2E32; border-radius: 15px;">
            <h5 class="card-title" style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 30px;">Quick Facts</h5>
            <div style="background-color: #212529; border-radius: 15px; padding: 15px;">
              <p class="card-text"><span style="color: #ffcc00;">Curfews:</span></p>
              <p class="card-text">Boston 9pm-6am</p>
            </div>
            <br>
            <div style="background-color: #212529; border-radius: 15px; padding: 15px;">
              <p class="card-text"><span style="color: #ffcc00;">National Guard Deployed:</span></p>
              <p class="card-text">None</p>
            </div>
            <br>
            <div style="background-color: #212529; border-radius: 15px; padding: 15px;">
              <p class="card-text"><span style="color: #ffcc00;">COVID-19 Stats for MA:</span></p>
              <p class="card-text">Cases: <span style="color: #64DD9B;">101,163</span></p>
              <p class="card-text">Deceased: <span style="color: #F65164;">7,085</span></p>
              <p class="card-text">Active: <span style="color: #FFC137;">Unknown</span></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <%- include('../../footer'); -%>
